<br>
essence of fire, crushed flame agate, imp blood (2 flame agates are first crushed by combining in a mortar &amp; pestle)<br>
<br>
Brewed. Trivial greater than 85, less than 102.<br>
<br>
Don't know wher the essence or the imp blood drops, but flame agates are dropped anywhere mid-level gems are dropped (black pearls, pearls, topaz, etc.). I think I had a few in the bank at one point in time, and they came from upper level animals in Stonebrunt.<br>
<br>
Edit: Hehe, scrolled down on the same page at EQtraders and came up with this info:<br>
<br>
essence of fire: guardian elementals in Solusek A, fire elementals in Lavastorm &amp; Najena, lava elementals in Sol B <br>
<br>
imp blood: fire imps in Lavastorm (hint: fire elementals will kill fire imps if they find the imps before you do, so be sure to go on killing sprees), imp protectors in Sol B (Nagafen's Lair) <br>
<br>
So there ya' go...<br>
<br>
Hope that helps,<br>
